<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en"
  style="font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; background-color: #fff8f3; color: #2d2d2d;">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Support Message</title>
</head>

<body
  style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: #fff; border: 1px solid #f2e2d6; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px;">
  <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 20px;">
    <img src="https://app.flexsirent.com/api/logo.png" alt="FlexsiRent Logo" style="max-height: 60px;" />
    <h2 style="color: #ab8c75; margin-top: 10px;">Support Message Received</h2>
  </div>
  <div style="padding: 10px 0;">
    <p style="font-size: 16px;">Dear Admin,</p>
    <p style="font-size: 15px;">
      You have received a new support message from a user through the FlexsiRent site. The details are as follows:
    </p>
  </div>
  <table style="width: 100%; font-size: 15px; background-color: #fdf9f7; padding: 15px; border-radius: 6px;">
    <tr>
      <td style="padding: 8px;"><strong>Name:</strong></td>
      <td style="padding: 8px;">{{name}}</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="padding: 8px;"><strong>Email:</strong></td>
      <td style="padding: 8px;">{{email}}</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="padding: 8px; vertical-align: top;"><strong>Message:</strong></td>
      <td style="padding: 8px;">{{message}}</td>
    </tr>
  </table>
  <div style="margin-top: 30px; font-size: 14px;">
    <p>Kind regards,</p>
    <p><strong>FlexsiRent</strong></p>
  </div>
</body>

</html>